@node Main "Midnight Blanker Document"

  Draws "strange" tree like "nodes" using breadth first algorithm.

  I actually am guilty of not being able to design an algorithm

  how I wanted, so I "mutated" it into this little thing.

  Kinda ugly isn't it?


